description.narrative: This activity (Technical Advisory Services - Social Communication) is a component of Girl Hub Ethiopia reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £8,689,374. This component benefits Ethiopia, and works in the following sector(s): Women's equality organisations and institutions. , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development, Deloitte, Overseas Development Institute, Oxford Policy Management, Population Council. The start date is 01-11-2011 and the end date is 31-08-2015.
